Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.08,0:01:15.35,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}我所不足的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.77,0:01:18.99,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}君が全部持ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.77,0:01:18.99,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}你却全部拥有
